{
  "stem": "9943.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he-- now, he wasn't going to sign that he's not-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] that he's not going to go back because otherwise, he has to accept Russian [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] citizenship.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, anyway, he was shipped off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Maybe, maybe it was even good that he was shipped off because maybe he was-- he was alive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Because if he would have gone back to Warsaw, then he would have probably had perished.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, whatever, that's a-- they did not tell the truth.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They just send him off.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a lot of people were sent off like that from, from Luck.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Luck had a lot of refugees.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Well, again, I'm going to jump ahead.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It came 1941, and I wanted to see Russia inside.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because whomever they brought, sent people-- supposedly communists and members of the Communist Party-- were ignoramuses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was really something that's unbelievable to compare-- to compare that the Soviet [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] intellectuals, or whatever-- supposedly.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I could tell stories, a lot of stories, about it how I, I recognized that the inadequacy of, of these people-- so just plain inadequates, ignoramuses.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I don't exaggerate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, anyway, so it came '41.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, I, I wanted to see Russia inside, how it is.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Is it different or not?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because that-- some of those that they send from Russia to, to instruct us were very well-- very well-educated people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Those that, that they send to work there were on a very low level.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But some of those that came from Kiev to, to give us some instruction were very educated people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I am easy on, on, on-- to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I like to travel, just as I said at the time when I wanted to be a physician.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
